\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Ro 6.6,11; Ep 4.19; 5.3-6\x*YaŇčdo, ji m…®kt…®m dakon aŇčpak morap butjikon toŇč uŇčun dapba k…®mak mudoni. Nak aŇčpak oden do yosot: yumabi aŇčpak mib…®l…® mib…®l…®, ae yo yokwi ak do but k…®ndap, ae yo morapm…® t…®m…®t do nandaba k…®k. UŇčun yo morapm…® t…®m…®t do nandak nandak uŇčun da ji kokup k…®dat gawak yomaŇč yaŇč asak.  
\v 6 PiŇčkop da m…®Ňčat am…®nyo aŇčpak uŇčuden aŇček geni d…®ma guram…®kgaŇč uŇčun tomni yokwisi yomd…®sak.  
